ment on the best GPA of all completed tertiary qualifications of the same level or higher.</p><p>In line with the university''s admissions policy and strategic plan, an assessment for admission may include competitively ranking applicants on the basis of specific academic achievement, English language proficiency and diversity factors. </p>',
